{"tid":757392,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大板京都之旅","createTime":"2018-07-26T21:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T09:09:14.000Z","uid":154419,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8845a6385e1ef9b2ee48e1070a25637b3f3eb439","tid":757392,"uid":154419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:50:39.000Z","msg":"第一日<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/054457_0ef89e67cb118f26ced02f3f0aab11b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F054457_0ef89e67cb118f26ced02f3f0aab11b6.png&h=d5af5dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出發去機場前睇到青馬大橋果邊有交通意外，成家轉搭地鐵，好彩預早發現，之後係東涌食個老早再入機場 <br />\n<br />\n啲老人家成日話早啲到機場係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁都比我遇到  冇得搭機場巴士入去"},{"pid":"e5582203ca777e035d3b0181e8446ed7ebc94e45","tid":757392,"uid":154419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/055159_0b3a611825084fd4d594f88e505bd0b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F055159_0b3a611825084fd4d594f88e505bd0b1.png&h=6bb8884e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/055326_72439084728f5e14f8a0af2e4d04ad75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F055326_72439084728f5e14f8a0af2e4d04ad75.png&h=995c50e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一落機見到既到比卡超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個場入面仲有兩部大電視比人玩PS4  唔趕時間真係想玩陣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11e3c1049b726fa29d68c10388fe9b16d213757","tid":757392,"uid":154419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T22:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係火撚滾者 原先住既民宿 通知我地要退錢比我地唔比住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩係搭車入去既時候 上網搵到另一間住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩炸唔係成家 都唔知住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  訓m記都似"},{"pid":"bea246afd2ddcea38b0e0afbeea30681a623b77e","tid":757392,"uid":64345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T22:10:37.000Z","msg":"見到啲錯字都唔想睇"},{"pid":"bc1314c1228f4d8b6087097e9aedee301b7c2401","tid":757392,"uid":158295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T22:11:05.000Z","msg":"有咩行程"},{"pid":"24356ede10242edf82be1371342c9c380f35a6ef","tid":757392,"uid":154419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T22:14:24.000Z","msg":"經過千辛萬苦有瓦遮頭之後 帶父王 母后去食好西先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/060910_734e759c67e6971f68d83f8dcf709f51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F060910_734e759c67e6971f68d83f8dcf709f51.png&h=d969e7e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係等緊食拉麵既時候遇上佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/201